@inject NavigationManager NavigationManager
<img src="images/planets/@($"planet{Planet.Index}.png")" alt="Planet-@Planet.Index" class="@(Planet.IsActive ? "cursor-pointer":"unactive-planet")" @onclick="@GoToPlanet"/>

@code {
    [Parameter]
    public Planet Planet { get; set; }

    [Parameter]
    public bool IsPlayMusic { get; set; }

    protected void GoToPlanet()
    {
        if (Planet.IsActive)
        {
            NavigationManager.NavigateTo($"/selection/{IsPlayMusic}/{Planet.Index}");
        }
    }

}
